Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰從現在起進入第三階段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.77,0:00:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體作戰人員請根據作戰時刻表
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好發艦準備
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向全員通話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將出發前往奪回
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被維甘搶佔的原聯邦軍月神基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦隊的任務是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.86,0:00:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開待機軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成機動戰士空降作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系統正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神輔助系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C浮游炮雙向通信系統確認正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘也許是十惡不赦的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.21,0:00:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我能聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.43,0:00:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些在火星圈痛苦掙扎的人們的吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請讓我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯隊 開始出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:00:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊的防禦火力分佈圖靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊可以提供的炮擊也極為有限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便這樣 也要在敵人作出應對前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佔領登陸陣地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 阿比斯隊出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇·阿比斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cnanche Custom 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.75,0:01:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會幫我 對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達AGE-FX 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用我的方式戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:34.76,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,800)}（一個月前）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來擺脫月亮二號的追兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貝也完好無損的到手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼值得擔心的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去見一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹是親兒子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了維甘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又能怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是爸爸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然活著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼扔下我和媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論有什麼理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然活著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不回來讓我們放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是伊澤爾坎特侵略地球的真正目的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他說要選出優秀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們移居地球 建立伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他簡直是個瘋子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他說這是拯救人類的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸怎麼看？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一件事我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球和維甘的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經走到無可挽回的地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在只有做力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了守護自己最寶貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個 要記得好好刷牙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們再也見不到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐接下來要去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個很危險的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小優
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們三個也要保重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 溫蒂也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫蒂 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重 溫蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴洛諾克 按計劃抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤諾亞姑姑 溫蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3個月沒見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 姑姑擔心死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該先跟這個人說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 你這孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你沒事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十三年不見了…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:07:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我 羅瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得和骨架一起換掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則不可能修成原來那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒打算把它修成原來那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接進化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進化成新的高達！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我你為什麼要去當宇宙海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言難盡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13年前 在戰鬥中身負重傷的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被宇宙海盜救起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,養傷期間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一起和海盜們共同生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏的生活讓我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭中隱藏的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指信息膠囊裏提到的EXA-DB嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是不僅限於此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍的腐敗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有迫使維甘走上戰爭之路的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星圈的殘酷現實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從得知這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法單純地把維甘視為敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就想去當置身事外的海盜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏 我找到了適合我的戰鬥方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫適合你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在為保護大家而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 站在一方的立場攻擊對手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後真的能守護心愛的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 戰鬥是無法避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果讓兩者的力量趨於均衡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪走維甘和聯邦軍執行作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所需的重要戰略物資和情報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止大規模戰鬥的爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我作為海盜力所能及的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要地球和維甘的實力均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭就會陷入膠著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有大量的犧牲者出現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠讓吉歐和羅瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所愛的那些人享受和平的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就會繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是癡人說夢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天不撲滅那些殺戮成性的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一天沒有和平！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有在這場戰爭中勝出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把維甘斬草除根一條路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道您會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的想法和父親不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會用我的方式去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是 我現在得出的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還會見面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你身體無恙就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要做這麼全面的檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不瞭解他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難保不會在你身體上做什麼手腳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還須檢查是否受到火星疫病的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘可能不像爺爺說得那樣 都是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論出於什麼理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:12:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們奪走了我們許多最寶貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星圈的人們也有苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓戰爭早日結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…到底被他們灌輸了些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的相信這是維甘奇怪行動的原因？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以戰爭為借口 選出所謂優秀人種
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把弱小者逐漸淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的目的無非是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只以消滅對方為目的的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是正確的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論究竟如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特是個瘋狂的獨裁者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他指揮下的維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了是可憎的敵國以外什麼都不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次作戰的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回月面上遺留的原聯邦基地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月神基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月神基地曾經是聯邦在月面的一大據點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在聯邦主力被大量遣往地球支援的間隙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不慎落入敵手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月神基地司令官 阿隆·西蒙斯叛變投敵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時有相當數量的間諜滲透進入基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在維甘發起攻擊的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地內的潛伏人員發動叛亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的兵力幾乎全軍覆滅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的月球基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被敵人利用作為進攻地球的補給站
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我們曾接到命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓天神號前往月神基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想來這可能也是敵人的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為阻止維甘進一步威脅地球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們決定將奪回月神基地的作戰計劃付諸實施
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛蒂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西想給我看？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高達嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據AGE-3在火星圈的戰鬥數據
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系統設計出的新機體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現前所未有的高速移動能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體進行了大幅輕量化改造
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 還追加了X-R專用小型支援部件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C浮游炮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是 最新型的高達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE-FX
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE-FX？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FX即是 X-R輔助型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專門為跟上X-R的戰鬥能力而設計
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以把它簡單理解成最強機體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛蒂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台高達的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以精確瞄準敵人機動戰士的某個部分吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然取決於機師的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但機體確實有這種潛力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是和你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:15:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許能夠實現我想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快和敵人接火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…到底想把我怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發出求救信號 等候營救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用我的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近月面 準備著陸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C浮游炮 展開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人也是人 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我會堅持我戰鬥的方式直到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 準備等離子潛航導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次出擊 我心裏一直有個疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是被禁止使用的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰同意搭載它們上船的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這徵得了艾倫格雷亞斯總司令的同意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那東西的威力太大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 您打算把基地一起毀了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野老司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是遵從章程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心存疑問的話可以去調查
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要親手殲滅維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到一個不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動過於單調會被吃透的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月神基地上出現高熱源反應
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人高熱源反應 消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C浮游炮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是無謀 魯莽的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有多少成功的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會陪著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再需要隱藏身份的維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就不再需要自爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 真打算不殺敵人結束戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夥兒 離月面著陸不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持警惕上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長 即將進入月球戰鬥空域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 這到底是吹得哪陣風？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月神基地如果不能重回聯邦之手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩者的均衡就會被打破
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘會源源不絕地向地球圈輸送兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是多麼龐大的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 你是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望是我杞人憂天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眾多敵人機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正降落基地周邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有這樣的大部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必大驚小怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的駐守兵力足以應付
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 你本可以躲起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.11,0:21:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入近距離防禦系統火力範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防禦系統 開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們在這裏做個了結
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派D區3架前往掩護巴魯德隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.40,0:21:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後續部隊 不許掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我瞧瞧 你的真本領
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的完成
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來需要托付給你了
